Josɛf ecʼɛrmij ebr Jesu eci mew owi ab ɛmKin Jesu Krist eci mew owi ecʼelel eke ɛcr. Josɛf ɛsu Jesu lis Mari; gbɛkↄ gbuŋ ke -lʼuwarir any a, Abŋ Lala ecʼabusu ɛm, Mari anŋ nimamn.
Ɛc Josɛf el ɛgŋ eke bʼɛlum Nyam ɛtŋ lʼerurm eke li kʼɛlu ow ↄkm dedeku fɛŋ ecʼany af; ow sosiɛm lʼɛgŋ lʼeb eke ew ew ɛm, li kʼɛlu ow es.<RF q=†>Jwifɛl ogŋ a, eke yↄw lele igŋ ab kʼɛbirm ɛtŋ -lʼɛru a, ow ecʼabr ɛnym a bʼɛw tuↄtuↄ (Ol Ɔkn 22.13-28). Mari eci lok ab owi ab ɛm a, Josɛf ↄtu eke kʼɛsŋʼn jɛj ok ɛm, ke li kók ow ɛ́s eke kʼocm ow es lís dedeku ecʼaraŋn. Ow ana ke li tutr eke li kʼɛlu ow es eke ów ɛsu owi kʼánm ɛm, ow ɛw pɛtɛ ɛm, ow e liy a kʼɛ́ym ↄkm (Ol Ɔkn 24.1).
Sica eke nʼam tutr low na a, Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ ecʼ <font color=blue>afr</font> ɛrm ɛs nyam ow mɛmn ɛm ɛŋnʼn ɛtŋ dadʼr ninɛ: «Josɛf, David eci lilaw, ɛrmij kʼókʼŋ eke kʼoc Mari ɛsɛ ŋ e yↄw af, aŋke Abŋ Lala ecʼabusu ɛm anake nʼanŋ nimamn a.
