Mʼam dad ↄny nawrɛ ɛm: <font color=blue>kokoba</font> ↄb ɛsɛl nↄnↄ lele agŋ ekʼij nɛny nyam Nyam ecʼany af ab a erur eke kʼɛkn low na eke am ɛkan a, kↄ -lʼɛknm, iri low na ekʼam irir a, kↄ -lʼirim.»<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn 1 Piɛr 1.10-12.
