Ɛm mʼel Abraham e Nyam, Isak e Nyam, lele Jakↄb e Nyam ab.»<RF q=†>Ɔkm Ok 3.6. Abraham, Isak lele Jakↄb ab uw ow ij akpo ekŋ yen yen sakp yen gbuŋ ɛtŋ Nyam am dad Mois odad na. Bɛ̀bmn Luk 20.37. Ow am yɛgm eke Abraham, Isak lele Jakↄb ab a, eke -lʼuw yɛji, -nʼanŋ owr ɛtŋ lɛgŋ nyam -li bʼow -lʼigb luw ɛm. Ɛtŋ Jesu usr af dad ninɛ: «Kↄ agŋ ekʼuw a e Nyam li kʼel ee? Njaŋ, lʼel agŋ ekʼuw ke anŋ owr a e Nyam.»
