Jɛj ok ɛs nyam lele iŋnyↄw nyam abƐmɛny Jesu dad in e jam ɛsɛl a nyandrɛ ɛm odad yɛgm ɛl ekʼow akpl ke sɛgŋ fɛŋ -ni ŋↄŋn Nyam, sos kʼↄ́wm ɛl es.
