Jesu lele Samari yↄwi ab ab<sup>(1-3)</sup> <font color=blue>Farisiɛl</font> iri wɛl am dad eke Jesu am ↄŋ wɛl am ok agŋ mij nuŋ nↄnↄ akm Jan, ɛtŋ nʼam ɛŋn <font color=blue>jam</font> ɛsɛl yɛji lʼakm ow. (Tasi ɛm a, Jesu in obi lʼokm ɛgŋ kaka mij nuŋ, kↄ in e jam ɛsɛl anake am ok agŋ mij nuŋ a.) Eke Jesu iri ów amua eke wɛl am dad a, nʼŋgboŋ Jude ɛtŋ lʼɛwl nʼim Galile.
