Ɛgŋ kaka kʼↄtum owm ɛm ogŋ eke ɛm Ɛs ekʼɛrmʼm a nyimnmʼn; ke sica ɛm, lɛgŋ es abal el ɛm a, mʼígbmʼn luw ɛm.
<font color=blue>Kokoba</font> ↄb ɛsɛl e silɛl ab ɛm e nyam ɛm wɛl nↄn: Nyam bʼow yɛgm ɛl fɛŋ low any uw.<RF q=†>Esayi 54.13. Ɛgŋ fɛŋ ekʼiri ɛm Ɛs ecʼodad ke ɛgŋ in e low yɛgm a e low eb a, ke ɛm ogŋ nʼam ow a.
