Ɛtŋ ɛmɛny Nyam Lɛl ɛjecʼam dad ɛsɛ: -Li bʼow -li lɛr ɛgŋ a eke -lʼupar mɛnɛgb ɛm a.<RF q=†>Zakari 12.10.
Jesu ecʼes oc owi<TS3><a href="tw://bible.*?40.27.57-61">Matie 27.57-61</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?41.15.42-47">Mark 15.42-47</a>; <a href="tw://bible.*?42.23.50-56">Luk 23.50-56</a>Ów amua bʼɛc a, Josɛf, Arimate baŋn iy a ow ibrm <font color=blue>Pilat</font> abusu eke kʼoc Jesu eci sos megl a.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Matie 27.58 ecʼakr otar a. Ke Josɛf a, Jesu eci <font color=blue>jam</font> ɛs kↄ es lↄl ɛm, aŋke li bʼuru Jwifɛl ecʼes ɛwɛl a. Pilat ↄŋʼn abusu lʼoc Jesu eci sos megl ab ab nʼim.
Nikodɛm a eke ncok nyam im ɛŋn Jesu a yɛji ow. Lʼism <font color=blue>kpey</font> eke wɛl wuwlm mijey ɛjecʼab ke ow eci leg a ↄtu eke kʼij kilo likŋ lele lɛw ab.
