Ɛtŋ ɛgŋ kaka fɛŋ eke kʼow irim kokoba ↄb ɛs na e low a, wɛl bʼow ogŋʼn Nyam ecʼagŋ a ecʼaraŋn ke wɛl íbiʼr.<RF q=†>Ol Ɔkn 18.15,18,19.
