Kpɛkŋ abu af ɛsɛl a ecʼes ɛw ɛs a lele in ecʼagŋ ab ab im ɛtŋ ot ɛrm ɛsɛl a ow. Gbɛkↄ -lʼɛwm lɛc ɛm, aŋke -nʼam uru eke bieku a ki wↄwl ɛl mebn.
Wɛl ↄny ɛrm ɛsɛl a im Sanedrɛn ecʼagŋ a ecʼany afSica eke -lʼotr wɛl -lʼowr a, -lʼot wɛl -nʼim <font color=blue>Sanedrɛn</font> ecʼagŋ a ecʼany af, ɛtŋ <font color=blue>egb</font> waw ɛs ligbɛl a am bibrm ɛl ów.
