-Lʼot agŋ ekʼam ij daŋku yadŋ ɛm ok Etiɛn af a yɛji -lʼow, ɛtŋ -nʼam dad -lʼɛsɛ: «Ɛgŋ na, wanci kpaŋ nɛny bʼanŋʼn ɛm nʼam dad ów eŋuŋ lʼok ɛy e <font color=blue>Nyamel</font> gbɛl lala na lele Mois ecʼ <font color=blue>ol</font> ab ab af!
