lʼeb lʼɛlu ow es gbre fɛŋ ɛm. Nʼↄŋ ow nuŋ ɛm ↄny ɛtŋ <font color=blue>Faraↄn</font> ekʼel Ejipt ecʼɛb ebu a ecʼany af, lʼakpal ow. Faraↄn ɛw Josɛf Ejipt ɛb a lel in ecʼakŋ a ecʼob fɛŋ ab ecʼes ɛw ɛs.
