Ɔny obi yɛji uwr any eke ow el ɛm e sabu ab ɛm mi kok juma mʼɛŋn yecʼekʼit a agŋ a ekʼam ɛwlʼm a, lele ɛm obi ab ecʼa.<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn Ob Kok 18.3a.
Sɛgŋ a fɛŋ mi yɛgm ↄny eke ki kokr juma ɛbɛn ke ɛ́lumn ↄgbↄru abu. Ɔ̀kan Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ Jesu eci sodad amua eke dad a: “Eke wɛl bʼↄŋ ɛgŋ ob a, wɛl bʼɛŋn sos ɛm iŋn nↄnↄ akm yecʼeke wɛl bʼɛŋn ɛgŋ ɛm a.” »<RF q=†>Jesu ecʼodad na, wɛl ocm ɛwm es Matie, Mark, Luk lele Jan ab eci lɛl ab ɛm.
Eke odad a uwr a, Pↄl ok ↄwrↄkp wus ɛl fɛŋ ab ŋↄŋn Nyam.
Agŋ a fɛŋ am ikŋ ↄŋn ɛtŋ am ɛy Pↄl af es ɛlulil eci.
Sos ↄw ɛl es nↄnↄ aŋke Pↄl dad ɛl eke wɛʼn kʼow in ɛknmʼn ij. Ɛtŋ -lʼɛwl ow toŋ -lʼok mijɛtŋ a e lís.
Pↄl aam JerusalɛmEke sica sʼɛlu ɛl es a, sʼimn mijɛtŋ ɛm eci, kpɛkŋ kpɛkŋ toŋ sʼok Kↄs lekr ɛm; lɛgŋ bʼɛny a, sʼim sʼok Rod lekr ɛm, ɛtŋ sʼigb yogŋ sʼim sʼok Patara baŋn.
Yogŋ, sʼɛŋn mijɛtŋ nyam ekʼam ow im Fenisi ɛtŋ sʼok ɛm sʼim.
Sʼɛkn Sipr lekr a kpekpe ɛm, sʼɛcr ow ecʼesr ɛm a, ɛtŋ sʼimn Siri eci. Sʼitr es Tir eci nanu gbɛl a, yogŋ a eke mijɛtŋ a kʼusm in ecʼɛrɛkp ab es a.
Yogŋ sʼɛŋn jam ɛsɛl ɛtŋ sʼanŋ ɛl ab ow ij nɛnɛgŋ mum nyam. Eke Abŋ Lala ɛwar ɛl a, -li dad Pↄl eke kʼúyum iim Jerusalɛm.
Gbɛkↄ eke nɛnɛgŋ gber mum a oc es a, sʼɛwl sʼebr ɛy ecʼusu im ab ɛm. Ɛl fɛŋ -lʼow -lʼɛwl ɛy, ɛl ecʼↄyↄw lele ɛl ecʼey ab toŋ sʼok ↄkm baŋn a. Okij nɛny yogŋ, sʼok ↄwrↄkp wus si ŋↄŋn Nyam.
Eke sica sʼɛlulil es a, sʼok mijɛtŋ ab ɛm ɛtŋ ɛl gbɛ -lʼɛwl -nʼim gbugŋ gbugŋ.
Sica eke sʼigb Tir a, sʼim sʼok Pitolemais, ɛtŋ sʼuwar ɛy ecʼusu im mij af ecʼa. Yogŋ sʼɛkanin ɛb ab ɛm ecʼagŋ lisijimɛl ab ab, ɛtŋ sʼanŋ ɛl ab lɛgŋ nyam cɛ.
Lɛgŋ bʼɛny a, sʼim sʼok Sesare. Yogŋ, sʼok Amani Mamn a ecʼes ↄmun ɛs Filip ecʼakŋ a ɛtŋ sʼanŋ in ogŋ a. Lʼel agŋ lↄbŋ a eke wɛl sↄsum ot Jerusalɛm a e nyam.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 6.5; 8.5.
Nʼↄny ey ↄyↄw yar eke ɛbim egŋ, ke bʼↄb <font color=blue>kokoba</font> dad odad eke Nyam bʼↄŋ ɛl a.
Sʼanŋ yogŋ ow kok sɛgŋ nↄnↄ toŋ ɛtŋ <font color=blue>kokoba</font> ↄb ɛs nyam eke wɛl bʼɛsŋ Agabus<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 11.28. anŋ Jude ow.
Eke sʼiri ów amua a, ɛy obi ɛy obi lele Sesare ecʼɛy lisijimɛl ab ab, si ŋↄŋn Pↄl eke kʼúyum iim Jerusalɛm.
Gbɛkↄ li dad ninɛ: «Kↄ bla sosiɛm ɛtŋ am ikŋn ↄŋn ↄwarʼm sos es ee? Ɛm, mi bɛbm sos, ow elm ɛm ecʼawŋ a cɛ eci, kↄ ke mʼúw Jerusalɛm Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ Jesu sosiɛm.»
Eke sʼↄtum sʼebmʼn odad ebl ɛm a, sʼatramʼn ij ɛtŋ si dad sʼɛsɛ: «Ke ow él yecʼa ekʼƐs Kↄtↄkↄ am erur a!»
Eke sica sʼanŋ yogŋ si kok sɛgŋ bɛb a, si bɛbm sos sʼam uyu sʼimn Jerusalɛm eci.
Sesare eci <font color=blue>jam</font> ɛsɛl a ow ɛwl ɛy Jerusalɛm; -lʼoc ɛy -nʼim ɛgŋ nyam eke kʼeb ok ɛy akŋ a ogŋ; wɛl bʼɛsŋʼn Minasↄn, Sipr lekr ɛm ecʼɛgŋ ekʼel jam ɛs lɛgŋ kpekpe, ke ir Jerusalɛm.
Yogŋ eke sʼok a, ɛy lisijimɛl a eb ɛy sos ɛm iŋn ɛm.
Pↄl im Jak ogŋ aEke lɛgŋ ɛny a, Pↄl ot ɛy ab im Jak ogŋ a; yogŋ, Nyamel ecʼ <font color=blue>agŋ</font> ekpekp a fɛŋ as luku.
Pↄl ɛsŋn ɛl, ɛtŋ mɛwl ɛm am dad ɛl in e juma ab ɛm ecʼów fɛŋ eke Nyam kok agŋ a ekʼelm Jwifɛl a ecʼaraŋn a.<RF q=†>Ow kʼↄdm Pↄl eci samani a eke am ↄŋ ɛl a, Azi wus af eci Sinyamel a eci ob ap a eke lʼeb a, nʼↄŋ wɛl. Ɛ̀kn 1 Korɛnt 16.1-4; Rom 15.25-28.
Eke -lʼirir ow ecʼodad a uwr a, -li kↄklm Nyam; ɛtŋ -li dad Pↄl ninɛ: «Ɛy lisijim, am ɛkn eke Jwifɛl fandi fandi ub Jesu nawrɛ, ke ɛl fɛŋ -li bʼucu ol a -nʼↄny es sɛnyn sɛnyn a.
Wɛl dad ɛl eke ŋ bi yɛgm Jwifɛl a fɛŋ ekʼin ir lutu a low eke wɛʼn kʼigŋ Mois ecʼ <font color=blue>ol</font> a in ɛlu es, ɛtŋ ɛmɛny ŋ bi dad wɛl eke wɛʼn kʼúbrm wɛl ecʼey a ekr es, wɛʼn kí kokm Jwifɛl ecʼów a.
-Li bʼow -lʼiri tasi eke ŋ ow aŋa. Ayaf si ki kokr ab ee?
Ow akpl ke kók ow a eke si bʼow si dadʼŋ a. Aŋa, sʼↄny agŋ yar ekʼij nɛny Nyam ecʼany af.
Òc ɛl ab im, ànŋ ɛl ab sos <font color=blue>ayal</font> eci low kok ab ɛm, ke sↄ́g ɛl e low kok a e labm, yecʼɛtŋ ke -lʼↄtu -lʼɛr sin.<RF q=†>Jwifɛl bɛb bʼij nɛny Nyam ecʼany af ɛdŋn lɛgŋ eb -li kʼɛgŋmn mar, -li kʼɛrmn sin. Pↄl ɛgŋ eb eke kʼel agŋ yar amua e low kok a ecʼidr ɛs. Ow sosiɛm, egb waw eke wɛl ibrm a (Awl 6.14-15), ow it ke li sↄ́g ow e labm. Sica sos ayal eci low kok a bʼuwr a, ow it ke lʼɛ́war Nyamel gbɛl ab ɛm eci egb waw ɛsɛl a, yecʼɛtŋ ke -li bɛbm sos egb waw a eci. Lɛgŋ ab af anake agŋ yar a bʼow ɛr sin, ke ofŋ sin a lele egb waw ab ab a. Ow ɛm a, agŋ a fɛŋ bʼow uw any eke ów a fɛŋ e wɛl dad ŋ e lís a elm nawrɛ; ow bʼow yɛgm eke ŋ yɛji anŋ Mois ecʼol a ecʼɛlum ɛm.
Agŋ a ekʼelm Jwifɛl ke ub nawrɛ a ecʼa, si kok lɛl sʼawŋ ɛl si dad ɛl ów yecʼa eke si bɛbm a. Kin ów a: -li kʼijmn ndey eke wɛl oc wawr egb ↄŋ sɛkp, -lʼɛgŋmn mebl, -lʼijmn ndey eke wɛl okm mebl es, -lʼijmn <font color=blue>nfaci</font>.»<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 15.20 lele ow ecʼakr otar ab ab.
Af yogŋ, Pↄl oc agŋ yar amua ab im, ɛtŋ eke lɛgŋ ɛny a, -nʼim wɛl ab sos ayal eci low kok ab ɛm.<RF q=†>Pↄl eci usu im ɛm a, ɛb ɛb a eke lʼɛc ɛm a ecʼagŋ a elm Jwifɛl; ow ↄŋ lʼaylm Nyam ecʼany af. Ow it eke li kʼayal sos gbuŋ ke lʼɛ́y Nyamel gbɛl ab ɛm. Low kok na bʼeb sɛgŋ lↄbŋ. Ɛmɛny nʼim Nyamel gbɛl ab ɛm ɛtŋ nʼam dad wɛl dedeku ɛm lɛgŋ yecʼaf eke sos ayal eci low kok a bʼow uwr ke wɛl bʼow waw ɛl ɛm ecʼɛgŋ nyam nyam ecʼegb a.<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn 1 Korɛnt 9.20.
Wɛl ɛdŋn Pↄl Nyamel gbɛl ab ɛmEke sos <font color=blue>ayal</font> eci sɛgŋ lↄbŋ a am ow uwr a, kpɛkŋ Azi ogog eci Jwifɛl a ɛkn Pↄl <font color=blue>Nyamel</font> gbɛl a e gbugŋ a. -Lʼij abra -nʼↄŋ dedeku a fɛŋ ɛtŋ -nʼↄny ow;
-nʼam ↄg -li dad -lʼɛsɛ: «Israɛl ecʼagŋ, ɛ̀lumn ɛy abu! Kin ɛgŋ a eke usu fɛŋ, agŋ fɛŋ ecʼany af bi dad ów eŋuŋ ok Israɛl ecʼagŋ af, Mois ecʼ <font color=blue>ol</font> ab af lele Nyamel gbɛl na af ab a. Ɛtŋ sicaca ɛm a, lʼot agŋ ekʼelm Jwifɛl lʼok Nyamel gbɛl ab ɛm;<RF q=†>lʼot agŋ ekʼelm Jwifɛl a lʼok Nyamel gbɛl ab ɛm:Ow itm eke agŋ ekʼelm Jwifɛl a kʼok Nyamel gbɛl a e gbugŋ lokm a. Ɛ̀kn Ezekiɛl 44.7. Yogŋ wɛl nↄn lɛl ekʼam dad ɛsɛ:Eke ɛgŋ ekʼelm Jwif afŋ ereb na es, ke in obi eci luw nʼam ↄl es a. ow ɛm a, -ni ŋuŋn usu lala a Nyam ecʼany af.»
Tasi ɛm a, -nʼam dad ɛbɛn aŋke -lʼɛkn Efɛs iy Trofim<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 20.4. Pↄl ab ɛb ab ɛm. -Nʼam tutr eke Pↄl oc ɛluʼl Nyamel gbɛl a e gbugŋ lokm a.
Likekr a eb es ɛb ab ɛm ɛtŋ ↄy ↄy a fɛŋ ɛm agŋ am anŋ ow. -Nʼↄny Pↄl -lʼↄdu -lʼɛlu ow ↄkm Nyamel gbɛl a e gbugŋ a ɛtŋ kpɛkŋ -li babl masany a.
-Nʼam ↄl eke -li kʼibi Pↄl, ɛtŋ kpɛkŋ wɛl im dad Rom e <font color=blue>kumada</font> a ekʼanŋ Jerusalɛm a likekr a eke eb es ɛb a fɛŋ ɛm a e low.
Kpɛkŋ lʼot srↄda eyŋ lele ɛl ecʼanym ɛsɛl ab ab ɛtŋ lʼuru es nʼim dedeku a ogŋ a. Eke -li bʼɛkn kumada a lele srↄda eyŋ ab ab a, -lʼↄrm Pↄl ij.
Kumada a ɛri im titm Pↄl, ↄŋ wɛl ↄnyʼn ɛtŋ ↄŋ abusu eke wɛl kʼoc ŋgbraka yony awŋnʼn; ɛtŋ lʼibrm ɛgŋ yecʼa eke lʼel a lele low yecʼa eke nʼam kok ab ab.
Gbɛkↄ dedeku ab ɛm, agŋ amua ám dad odad na, ke bɛb ám dad ɛjeci. Kumada a ↄ́tum irim low a tasi likekr na ɛm; nʼↄŋ abusu eke wɛl kʼoc Pↄl im in eci frutu lakp ab ɛm.
Eke Pↄl anŋ êl a ecʼaf uyu usu a, srↄda eyŋ a ocʼr abu ɛm abu ɛm, dedeku a e lɛc ekʼam ɛlu ↄkm a sosiɛm,
aŋke agŋ a fɛŋ am usʼr jam ↄg dad ɛsɛ: «Wɛl íbiʼr! Wɛl íbiʼr!»
Pↄl ibrm odadWanci ab af eke srↄda eyŋ a am ↄl eke kʼↄny Pↄl ɛlu frutu lakp ab ɛm a, li dad <font color=blue>kumada</font> a ninɛ: «Kↄ mʼↄny abusu eke mi ki dadʼŋ odad tɛl ee?» Kumada a ninɛ: «Kↄ bʼɛbr <font color=blue>Grɛk</font> ee?
Njɛ elm Ejipt iy a eke efnɛny a cɛ is ar ke ot áru fandi yar ab im loj ab ee?»<RF q=†>Lɛgŋ ab ɛm a, Rom am ↄny ses babur nↄnↄ Jude eke li kʼɛw es ab ɛm. Low ɛ́gŋm ebm ɛsɛl nↄnↄ anŋ eke bʼat Rom low.
Pↄl dad ninɛ: «Ɛm Jwif, wɛl ewʼm Tars ɛb ɛm, Silisi wus af, ɛb ekʼↄny any ecʼɛgŋ. Mʼam ŋↄŋnʼŋ, ↄŋʼm abusu mi dád dedeku a odad.»
Kumada a ↄŋʼn abusu. Pↄl inym es êl a ecʼaf uyu usu a ɛtŋ lʼↄwl wɛl abu eke -li ki yewal. Eke -li yewalil a, Pↄl am dad ɛl odad <font color=blue>Ebre</font> ɛm:<RF q=†>Ebre ɛbr ɛm:odad na Grɛk ɛm a, wɛl ↄtu ekʼitŋn ɛjecʼɛm dad ɛsɛArame ɛbr ɛm.
Eke sica -lʼirir ekʼow am dad ɛl odad Ebre ɛm a, usu a irm es tiŋ ɛtŋ Pↄl dad ninɛ:
«Ɛm Jwif, wɛl ewʼm Tars ɛb ɛm, Silisi wus af, gbɛkↄ Jerusalɛm aŋa wɛl gbagblʼm, ɛtŋ Gamaliɛl el ɛm e low yɛgm ɛs.<RF q=†>Gamaliɛl:ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 5.34 lele akr otar ab ab. Li yɛgmʼm mʼuw ɛy lagŋɛl ecʼol ab any sɛnyn sɛnyn. Nyam eci juma kok a eci lɛc a iyʼm ɛm nↄnↄ ɛsɛ elel eke yɛfɛnyna ↄny fɛŋ ow iy ↄny ɛm ab af.
Mʼijr agŋ a ekʼam us Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ Jesu ecʼejagb na a gbre luw eci. Mʼↄny egŋ lele ↄyↄw ab mʼok sobel ɛm.
<font color=blue>Egb</font> waw ɛs ligbɛl a lele <font color=blue>Sanedrɛn</font> a nimum ab ↄtu ekʼij daŋku ekʼow el odad nawrɛ eke mʼam dad. Ɛl ecʼabu ɛm, mʼɛŋn silɛl ɛy lisijimɛl Jwifɛl ekʼanŋ Damas a eci eke ow ɛm -li kʼuwrʼm any; ɛtŋ mʼim eke mi kʼↄny ↄmn ɛsɛl a ekʼanŋ a, mʼók ɛl ŋgbraka ke mʼót ɛl ab mʼow Jerusalɛm ke mi kók ɛl low ŋuŋ.»<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 8.3; 9.1-2.
Pↄl am dad in ecʼɛrm ɛm itŋn a ecʼodad«Mʼus ejagb mʼaam ɛtŋ eke mʼam titm Damas a, lɛgŋ uyu nuŋ ɛm, kpɛkŋ usuayl ligbɛl nyam eci jɛjn a anŋ afr ow uburʼm es.
Mʼɛy wus ɛtŋ mʼiri lebl nyam ekʼam dadʼm ɛsɛ: “Sↄl, Sↄl, kↄ bla ɛtŋ am ijrʼm gbre ee?”
Mʼibrm mʼɛsɛ: “Ɛgŋ gbɛl, kↄ ŋ bwo elʼŋ ee?” Lebl a dad ninɛ: “Ɛm Nasarɛt e Jesu ekʼam ijr gbre a.”
Agŋ a ekʼanŋ ɛm ab a ɛkn usuayl a, kↄ -lʼirim ɛgŋ a ekʼam dadʼm odad a e lebl a.
Mʼibrm mʼɛsɛ: “Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ, ayaf mi ki kokr ab ee?” Ɛtŋ li dadʼm ninɛ: “Ìgb wus, ìm Damas, yogŋ wɛl bʼow dadʼŋ low yecʼeke Nyam am dadʼŋ eke ki kok a.”
Eke usuayl na ekʼam jɛjn a efalʼm any a, agŋ a ekʼanŋ ɛm ab a ↄnyʼm abu ɛtŋ ɛwlʼm Damas.
Yogŋ, ɛgŋ nyam anŋ eke wɛl bʼɛsŋ Ananias, <font color=blue>Nyam</font> nuŋ igŋ ɛs sɛnyn eke bʼɛlum ɛy ecʼol a, ke Damas e Jwifɛl a fɛŋ bʼerur in e low.
Lʼow nʼɛŋnʼm, li titmʼm ɛtŋ li dadʼm ninɛ: “Ɛm lisijim Sↄl, ɛ̀kn es!” Wanci ab af cɛ, any efl a oc es ɛtŋ mʼam ɛknʼn.
Lʼigŋ af li dad ninɛ: “Ɛy lagŋɛl e Nyam a ikŋ anym sↄsum ocʼŋ yecʼɛtŋ ke úw low yecʼa eke lʼerur ab any, ɛ́kn Nɛnyɛmbri Nyam Ɛs a, ke íri in obi e nɛny ɛm ecʼodad.
Tasi ɛm a, ow it eke kʼij in e daŋku yecʼɛtŋ ke agŋ a fɛŋ ecʼany af, dád low yecʼa ekʼɛkn ke iri a.
Ɛtŋ sica bla sosiɛm kʼeku ee? Ìgb, òk mij nuŋ, ke ŋ eci sikpl a fɛŋ tɛ́tŋ es in e nin a ecʼɛsŋ ɛm.”
Mʼɛwl mʼim Jerusalɛm, ɛtŋ eke mʼam ŋↄŋn Nyam <font color=blue>Nyamel</font> gbɛl a e gbugŋ a, mʼɛkan nuŋ ɛm.
Mʼɛkn Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ ɛtŋ li dadʼm ninɛ: “Ògŋ es ɛy ↄkm Jerusalɛm fafa, aŋke ɛm e lís e low a eke am dad a, ɛb eyŋ a kʼow ɛgŋm ow e low ebm.”
Mi dad mʼɛsɛ: “Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ, -lʼuw any tasi eke mi bʼim <font color=blue>Nyam</font> nuŋ igŋ susu mʼↄny agŋ mʼok sobel ɛm ɛtŋ mi bʼↄŋ wɛl ↄr agŋ eke bʼubʼŋ nawrɛ a.
Ɛtŋ lɛgŋ a eke wɛl ibi ŋ e daŋku ij ɛs Etiɛn a, ɛm yɛji mʼanŋ yogŋ. Agŋ a ekʼam ibi Etiɛn a, mʼɛgŋ ɛl e low a mʼeb ɛtŋ mʼↄsu ɛl e mob sus ɛm a.”<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Ob Kok 7.58; 8.1.
Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ dadʼm ninɛ: “Ìm, aŋke mʼow mʼɛrmʼŋ usu kpekpe, agŋ a ekʼelm Jwifɛl a ogŋ.” »
