Pↄl am ibrm eke Agripa kʼub nawrɛEke Pↄl am dad ów in e sos dogŋn ecʼa, Fɛstus barmʼn es lebl tuↄtuↄ ɛm ninɛ: «Pↄl, nuŋ ɛm am uŋʼŋ! Wewr lɛl nↄnↄ toŋ ow am ɛwʼŋ nuŋ ɛm uŋ!»
