Wɛl am ɛwl Pↄl RomSica wɛl ɛgŋ eb eke si bʼow sʼim Itali mijɛtŋ ɛm eci. Wɛl oc Pↄl lele sobel ɛm ɛsɛl ɛjeci bɛb ab abul srↄda eyŋ ekŋ yen ecʼanym ɛs nyam eke wɛl bʼɛsŋ Julius. Lʼel Rom eci srↄda eyŋ a ecʼeb a eke wɛl bʼɛsŋ “Sesar Ogust eci eb” a ecʼanym ɛs.
