Sʼirmn lɛgŋ nↄnↄ, ɛtŋ mij us a yɛji am ɛw tuↄtuↄ aŋke lakpo am uwr.<RF q=†>lakpo am uwr:Grɛk ɛm ecʼelel eke wɛl bʼirir elnɛny ɛnŋ e lɛgŋ.Ow el Sikpl oc ap ecʼes gbɛgbl eke bʼɛy awl libarm ɛm oglog awl lɛw ɛm Jerusalɛm. Awl amua af lɛf ɛgbɛl bʼɛlu, ow bʼↄŋ mij fɛŋ ecʼubr a bʼɛw tuↄtuↄ. Ow sosiɛm Pↄl am ɛwar ɛl dad ɛsɛ:
