Ŋ ntotŋ bʼokʼŋ ol ekʼↄny a eci, gbɛkↄ ɛ́luam ol, ow bʼↄŋ ↄny Nyam ecʼany a oc es.
Tasi ɛm, kin yecʼeke wɛl bʼawl Nyam Lɛl ɛm: ↄny sosiɛm, agŋ a eke elm Jwifɛl a bi yayr Nyam e nin a.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Esayi 52.5, Sɛptant ɛm ecʼodad eke wɛl oc.
Eke bi kok low yecʼa eke ol bi dad a, ke nawrɛ tasi <font color=blue>likr</font> es ubr el low akplu. Kↄ eke ɛ́luam ol, ɛtŋ ubr likr es bↄbↄ yɛji, anŋ ɛsɛ ɛgŋ eke ubrm es ab af.
Kin low nyam: ɛgŋ nyam ubrm likr es, gbɛkↄ li bʼɛlum Nyam ecʼol a. Kↄ Nyam kʼow ɛgŋm ebmʼn ɛsɛ likr cɛ owʼn ubr es af ee?
Ɛgŋ ikŋ na ubrm sos megl af e likr es, gbɛkↄ li bʼɛlum ol. Eke ow el ɛbɛn a, in anake li bʼow li jɛj ŋ owi lʼok, ŋ eke ɛluam ol a. Ke ŋ nana ↄny ol a eke wɛl nↄn a lele likr es ubr ab!
Tasi ɛm a, Jwif tasi a, elm ɛgŋ a eke bʼan es sos megl af ɛsɛ Jwif af a, ɛtŋ likr es ubr tasi a yɛji, elm sos lɛl a eke wɛl bʼubr es a.
Kↄ Jwif tasi a, in lʼel ɛgŋ a eke el Jwif ɛrm ɛm a, ɛtŋ likr es ubr tasi a, el ɛrm ɛm ecʼa.<RF q=†>Jeremi 4.4; 9.24-25; Ol Ɔkn 30.6. Likr es ubr na, Nyam ecʼAbŋ ab ɛm li bʼanŋ lʼow, kↄ ow elm ol eke wɛl nↄn ab ɛm. Jwif tasi a ɛ́ŋnm in ecʼaw a agŋ ɛm, kↄ Nyam ɛm li bʼɛŋn.
