Nyam sↄsum Israɛl eyŋ ocƐm mʼel Krist eci, ow sosiɛm, low a eke mʼam mʼow mi dad a el low nawrɛ, mi kʼↄtum mʼↄnym yadŋ. Ɛm e tutr a eke Abŋ Lala am nyimn a yɛji am dadʼm eke ow el low nawrɛ.
Ɛm ecʼɛrm a sos ↄw es nↄnↄ ligbɛl ɛtŋ mʼam ij gbre eke úwrm.
Mi bʼow mʼɛgŋ mʼeb eke Nyam kʼigŋ ↄwlʼm ke mi kpáb es Krist e lís, eke ow ↄtu cɛ eke kʼeb ɛm lisijimɛl Jwifɛl ɛlu es.
Bla ecʼee? -Lʼel Israɛl eyŋ, Nyam ot ɛl -lʼel ow ecʼey. Wɛl ecʼaraŋn nʼanŋ in ecʼanygbɛl ab ɛm, lʼɛgŋ <font color=blue>sinm</font> wɛl ab, nʼↄŋ wɛl in ecʼol a, li yɛgm wɛl sɛwl yecʼɛm eke wɛl kʼigŋʼn nuŋ a, ɛtŋ li dad wɛl ów eke li bɛbm lʼɛw es wɛl ecʼa.
Ɛl -lʼel ɛl lagŋɛl ekpekp a eci alaw.<RF q=†>ɛl lagŋɛl ekpekp a:el Abraham, Isak, Jakↄb lele in ecʼey ab ab. Ɛl ecʼaraŋn anake wɛl ew Krist ɛsɛ ɛgŋ owr af, in eke lʼel Nyam ekʼanŋ ob fɛŋ e nuŋ af a! Kↄklm él in eci sɛgŋ fɛŋ! Amɛn!
Nyam ecʼey tasi eke sↄsum otOw elm ke wɛl dad ɛsɛ Nyam e low a eke ɛwar ɛw es a ɛlu ok es. Tasi ɛm a, agŋ a eke wɛl ew ɛy lagŋ Israɛl ɛm a, ɛl fɛŋ -lʼelm Israɛl eyŋ tasi.
Ɛtŋ agŋ a bↄbↄ eke wɛl ew ɛy lagŋ Abraham ecʼeb ab ɛm a yɛji, ow elm ɛl fɛŋ -lʼelm ow ecʼey tasi, aŋke Nyam dad Abraham ninɛ: Isak ɛm anake bʼow ɛŋn alaw eke bʼow ɛlu ŋ e nin a ↄkm a.<RF q=†>Nuŋ Ɔb 21.12.
Kin sodad na ecʼiri tasi a: ow elm ey a eke wɛl ew igŋ nyam lele yↄw nyam ab ecʼerur ɛm a elm Nyam ecʼey. Kↄ ey tasi a, ɛl -lʼel Nyam ecʼɛwar ecʼey a.
Kin ɛwar a e sodad a: mʼow mʼɛwl mɛny mʼow ŋ ogŋ a lakpo yecʼa, lɛgŋ nɛnɛ af, ɛtŋ ayŋ Sara bʼow ew iy igŋ nyam.<RF q=†>Nuŋ Ɔb 18.10.
Ɛtŋ ow elm na sↄny cɛ: kↄ Rebeka ecʼa yɛji. Lʼew ey yony ɛy lagŋ Isak ab.
<sup>(11-13)</sup> Ey yony a, wɛl kʼewm kokm ɛl wus, -li ki kokm low ŋuŋ oglog low nimamn. Gbɛkↄ Nyam dad Isak ɛw es eke: likpekp a bʼow anŋ jam ɛs a eci es ɛw ɛm.<RF q=†>Nuŋ Ɔb 25.23. Ɛtŋ usu ɛjecʼɛm a, Nyam Lɛl dad ninɛ: mʼerur Jakↄb mʼoc ɛtŋ mi wal Esayu mʼɛlu es.<RF q=†>Malaki 1.2-3. Low na ɛcr nɛnɛ, yecʼɛtŋ ke Nyam e low a eke bɛbm ɛw es a ɛ́li any. Nyam bi sↄsum agŋ ot ɛsɛ elel eke li bʼerur ab af, ɛtŋ sↄsum oc a elm agŋ a ecʼów e bi kok a sosiɛm, kↄ Nyam cɛ eke bʼɛsŋ ɛgŋ ab ɛm ow bʼanŋ ow.
