Tasi ɛm a, li dad Mois ninɛ: Mi bʼow mʼikŋ ɛgŋ e mʼerur eke mi kʼikŋ sↄrŋ a sↄrŋ, ɛtŋ mi bʼow mʼↄnyn ɛgŋ eke mʼerur eke mi kʼↄnyn ɛrm mamn a ɛrm mamn.<RF q=†>Ɔkm Ok 33.19.
Ow sosiɛm a, Nyam e sↄrŋ ikŋ a ánm agŋ e low e bʼerur ab ɛm, oglog sos eke bʼatr es ab ɛm, kↄ Nyam cɛ eke ↄny sↄrŋ ikŋ ab ɛm ow bʼanŋ ow.
Nyam Lɛl ɛm, Nyam dad Ejipt ecʼɛb ebu a ninɛ: Mʼɛwʼŋ ɛb ebu, yecʼɛtŋ ke ŋ ɛm mʼɛ́lu ɛm ecʼabusu a ↄkm, ke mi kók ɛm e nin a eb es wus na nimum af.<RF q=†>Ɔkm Ok 9.16, Sɛptant ɛm ecʼodad eke wɛl oc.
Wɛl bʼɛkn eke Nyam bʼikŋ ɛgŋ eke lʼerur eke li kʼikŋ sↄrŋ a sↄrŋ, ɛtŋ li bʼↄtur ɛgŋ eke lʼerur eke li kʼↄtur ɛrm a ɛrm.
Nyam bi sↄsum agŋ ot ɛsɛ elel eke li bʼerur ab afGbɛkↄ, kʼaw ke ɛgŋ íbrm im ɛsɛ: sica, eke ow el nɛnɛ, bla sosiɛm ɛmɛny Nyam kʼɛnym ɛy abr ee? Bwo ecʼɛgŋ ↄtu eke ki dogŋn low eke li bʼerur ab ee?
Kↄ ŋ gbɛ, bwo elʼŋ eke kʼatar Nyam ab ee? Kↄ mijel bʼibrm ɛgŋ a eke kokʼr a ɛsɛ: bla sosiɛm ɛtŋ kokʼm mijel ee?<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn Esayi 29.16; 45.9.
Kↄ mijel kok ɛs ↄtum eke ki kok low e lʼerur kpeŋ ab ab ee? Kↄ lʼↄtum eke kpeŋ nyam a cɛ, li kʼitl li kok lɛ́w sↄbↄ nyam oglog lɛ́w kprakasa nyam ee?
Nyam erur eke kʼɛlu in ecʼɛrm bebl ↄkm ke yɛ́gm in ecʼabusu a. Gbɛkↄ agŋ a eke nʼↄny ɛrm bebl wɛl ab, ke it eke kʼirm ↄgbu es a, lʼɛgŋ wɛl e low lʼeb low eku ligbɛl ɛm.
Lʼɛgŋ low nɛnɛ lʼeb, yecʼɛtŋ ke lʼɛ́lu in eci anygbɛl a e sagb a ↄkm agŋ eke lʼerur eke li ki yɛgm in e sↄrŋ ikŋ a e lís. Ow el agŋ a eke lʼikŋ anym li bɛbm lʼɛw es eke kʼɛŋn anygbɛl na a.
Ɛtŋ ɛy sʼel agŋ amua eke lʼɛsŋ a. Ow elm Jwifɛl ecʼaraŋn cɛ lʼɛsŋm ɛy, kↄ agŋ eke elm Jwifɛl ecʼaraŋn ecʼagŋ a yɛji.
Nyam dad low na kokoba ↄb ɛs Ose e lɛl ab ɛm:Agŋ a eke elm ɛm ecʼagŋ a,mi bʼow mʼɛsŋ ɛl “ɛm ecʼagŋ”.Ɛtŋ agŋ a eke mʼérurm a,mi bʼow mʼɛsŋ ɛl “agŋ e mʼerur”.
Ɛtŋ yogŋ a eke wɛl dad agŋ eke:«Ɔny elmn ɛm ecʼagŋ a,»wɛl bʼow ɛsŋ ɛl Nyam ekʼanŋ owr ecʼey.<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn Ose 2.1-3; 2.25.
Esayi, in am ɛlu lebl Israɛl ecʼagŋ e lís ɛsɛ:Eke batŋ Israɛl eyŋ ɛny nↄnↄ ɛsɛ okij any e mirici af yɛji,agŋ tɛl a eke wal es a cɛ bʼow ɛŋn sel.
Tasi ɛm a, Nyam Admaga bʼow kok low a eke li dad a wus af aŋa,li bʼow li kok fafa toŋ lʼigŋ nuŋ.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Esayi 10.22-23. Akr 27 toŋ akr 33 ab ɛm a e sodad a, Pↄl ot kokoba ↄb ɛs Esayi e sodad a eke dad a ɛsɛ elel eke wɛl bʼɛŋn Sɛptant ɛm ab af.
Ɛtŋ low na anake Esayi yɛji ikŋ anym dad a:blel Nyam Abusu Ɛs okm ɛy alaw bɛb es,ke blel sʼánŋ ɛsɛ Sodↄm eyŋ af,ke sʼótarir es Gomↄr eyŋ ab.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Esayi 1.9, ke ɛ̀kn Nuŋ Ɔb 19.23-28 yɛji.
Ke Israɛl ecʼagŋ a am ↄl eke kʼel nyim nyim eke -li bʼɛlum Nyam ecʼol a sosiɛm. Kↄ ɛl -lʼↄwl -lʼok es.
Bla sosiɛm ee? -lʼↄwl -lʼok es, aŋke -lʼↄlm nyim nyim el na es ↄmn ɛm, -li tutr eke ɛl ecʼów kok ɛm -li bʼow -nʼɛŋn. Ɛbɛn a, -lʼuyum lebn a eke bʼɛlu ɛgŋ wus ab ab.
Tasi ɛm a, Nyam Lɛl dad ninɛ:Siↄn ɛb ɛm, mʼam ɛw lebn nyam eke bʼeb agŋ akr,lob eke bʼɛlu ɛgŋ wus es.Ɛgŋ yecʼeke bʼoc ↄmn ɛluʼl ɛm a,sos kʼow ↄwm es lɛgŋ kaka.<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn Esayi 8.14; 28.16.
Jwifɛl lele agŋ eke elm Jwifɛl ab ab ↄny Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ nyamAgŋ lisijimɛl, mʼam erur ɛm ecʼɛrm fɛŋ ɛm eke Jwifɛl kʼɛŋn sel, ɛtŋ mʼam ibrm Nyam low na ɛl eci.
Nawrɛ, mʼↄtu eke mi kʼij ɛl e lís e daŋku mʼɛsɛ: Nyam e kok owi anŋ ɛl ɛrm ɛm tasi, kↄ -lʼuwm ow ecʼejagb ab any tasi.
-Lʼirim elel eke Nyam bʼocr agŋ nyim nyim a, ɛtŋ -lʼↄl ɛl ecʼelel eke agŋ bʼeel nyim nyim ab es. Ow ↄŋ -lʼɛgŋm -lʼebm elel a eke Nyam bʼocr agŋ ɛsɛ agŋ nyim nyim af a.
Tasi ɛm a, Krist kok Mois ecʼol a e low iy nɛny, yecʼɛtŋ ke Nyam óc agŋ fɛŋ eke bʼub Krist nawrɛ a agŋ nyim nyim.
Mois in obi nↄn elel eke wɛl ↄtu eke kʼeel nyim nyim ol ecʼɛlum sosiɛm a ninɛ: ɛgŋ yecʼeke bi kok ol ecʼów a fɛŋ ekʼanŋ ɛm a, bʼow anŋ owr in ɛm.<RF q=†>Ob Ap 18.5.
Gbɛkↄ kin yecʼeke li dad agŋ a eke Nyam bʼoc ɛsɛ agŋ nyim nyim af ɛl ecʼↄmn a sosiɛm a e lís: kì dad ŋ ecʼɛrm ab ɛm kʼɛsɛ: bwo ecʼɛgŋ bʼow uyu afr ee? Ɛsɛ ɛbɛn eke wɛl am ibrm, kↄ bwo bʼow uyu afr ↄny Krist usm es ee?
Ɛmɛny kì dad kʼɛsɛ: bwo ecʼɛgŋ bʼow us es wus lokm ee? Ɛsɛ ɛbɛn eke wɛl am ibrm, kↄ bwo bʼow us es yogŋ ↄny Krist ɛlu ↄkm agŋ ekʼuw ab ɛm ee?
Ow elm ɛbɛn, aŋke wɛl nↄn: odad a anŋʼŋ saw, ŋ e nɛny ab ɛm lele ŋ ecʼɛrm ɛm ab ab.<RF q=†>Ol Ɔkn 30.12-14. Ɛtŋ odad na, in anake lʼel ↄmn ecʼamani a eke sʼam ↄb a.
Eke ŋ e nɛny bi dad agŋ fɛŋ ecʼany af ɛsɛ Jesu el Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ,<RF q=†>Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ:Grɛk ɛm aKuriↄs. Sica eke Jwifɛl a erur eke kʼitŋn Amani Sig a eke wɛl nↄn Ebre ɛm a, Grɛk ɛm a, Nyam eci nin a eke ij Ebre ɛm, ke el YAHWEH (Admaga), -nʼↄny -lʼitŋn ow elKuriↄs(Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ). Aŋa wɛl am ɛgŋ eb eke Jesu in obi a el Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ. ɛtŋ ub nawrɛ ŋ ecʼɛrm ab ɛm eke Nyam igbmʼn luw ɛm a, ow bʼow ↄŋʼŋ ɛŋn sel.
Tasi ɛm a, eke si bʼub nawrɛ ɛy ecʼɛrm fɛŋ ɛm a, Nyam bʼoc ɛy ɛsɛ agŋ nyim nyim af, ɛtŋ eke si bʼɛlu ɛy ecʼↄmn a ↄkm agŋ fɛŋ ecʼany af a, li bi sↄg ɛy.
Ɛɛ, Nyam Lɛl dad ninɛ: Ɛgŋ yecʼeke bʼoc ↄmn ɛluʼl ɛm a, sos kʼow ↄwm es lɛgŋ kaka.<RF q=†>Esayi 28.16, Sɛptant ɛm ecʼodad eke wɛl oc. Esayi e lɛl ab ɛm e sodad eke wɛl bʼɛŋn Rom nuŋ 10 na ɛm a, Sɛptant ɛm wɛl ot.
Ow sosiɛm a, ereb anm Jwifɛl lel agŋ ekʼelm Jwifɛl ab ab ecʼaraŋn ij. Ɛl fɛŋ Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ nyam cɛ -nʼↄny, ɛtŋ li bʼↄŋ agŋ a fɛŋ eke bʼɛluʼl lebl a in ecʼów amamn a.
Nyam Lɛl dad ninɛ: Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ bʼow sↄg agŋ a fɛŋ eke bʼow ɛluʼl lebl a.<RF q=†>Joɛl 3.5.
Amani Mamn e kokoba ecʼↄbSica ayaf -li bʼow -lʼɛlul Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ lebl, eke -lʼubm ow nawrɛ ee? Ɛtŋ ayaf -li bʼow -lʼub ow nawrɛ, eke -lʼirim ow e lís owi ee? Ɛtŋ ɛmɛny ayaf -li bʼow -lʼiri ow e lís owi, eke ɛgŋ ↄbm ɛl ow ecʼamani ee?
Ɛtŋ ayaf ɛgŋ kʼↄbr ow ecʼamani, eke wɛl ɛram ɛgŋ ow ecʼee? Ow sosiɛm wɛl nↄn Nyam Lɛl ɛm: Ɛbɛn tasi eke ow akpl eke wɛl ki lɛr agŋ a eke bʼↄb samani amamn a eci mowrer ana!<RF q=†>Esayi 52.7.
Gbɛkↄ, ow elm agŋ a fɛŋ ɛluam Amani Mamn a. Tasi ɛm a, Esayi dad ow e low ninɛ: Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ, kↄ bwo ecʼɛgŋ ub ɛy e Nyam odad a nawrɛ ee?<RF q=†>Esayi 53.1.
Njɛ, eke ɛgŋ bʼiri amani a, ow anake li bʼub Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ nawrɛ a, ɛtŋ amani na, ow ow el Krist e lís ecʼodad a.
Ow sosiɛm mʼam ibrm mʼɛsɛ: kↄ Jwifɛl amua, -lʼirim odad na e low ee? Yadŋ, -lʼiri! Tasi ɛm a, Nyam Lɛl dad ninɛ:Wɛl iri ɛl e lebl wus nimum afɛtŋ ɛl e sodad ebl im toŋ ok wus e nuŋ.<RF q=†>Selu 19.5, Sɛptant ɛm ecʼodad eke wɛl oc.Ɛl e lebl... ɛl e sodad...:Selu na ɛm a, ow el Nyam e mob e kok anŋ afr a e daŋku ekʼij. Pↄl am oc selu na ecʼodad ebl a bɛbmn Krist e jam us ɛsɛl ecʼAmani Mamn a eke kʼoc im ↄmun es susu susu fɛŋ ab ab.
Ow sosiɛm ɛmɛny mʼam ibrm mʼɛsɛ: Kↄ Israɛl ecʼagŋ na, -li kʼirim low a kʼokm ɛl es sos ɛm ee? Ke Mois ikŋ anym dad ɛl Nyam ecʼodad a ninɛ:Mi bʼow mʼↄŋ nyamn ɛyr ↄny ↄny agŋ na ekʼel agŋ ekʼↄnym any a e lís.Mi bʼow mʼↄŋ ɛrm ebl ↄnyagŋ ekʼↄnym low any uw kaka a e lís.<RF q=†>Ol Ɔkn 32.21.
Ɛtŋ Esayi oc lokm susu ɛm dad ninɛ: kin low eke Nyam dad:Agŋ a eke ↄlmʼm es a, ɛl -nʼɛŋnʼm.Ɛtŋ mʼɛlu sos ↄkm mi yɛgm agŋ a eke ibram imlow kaka a.<RF q=†>Esayi 65.1.
Gbɛkↄ Israɛl ecʼagŋ a e lís a, Nyam dad ninɛ:Lɛgŋ nimum a,mʼɛgŋm abu es bieku nyameke ɛ́luam low, ke ɛ́gŋm ɛm e low ebm a e lís.<RF q=†>Esayi 65.2.
Nyam igŋm Israɛl eyŋ ɛlum esSica mʼam ibrm mʼɛsɛ: kↄ Nyam in ecʼagŋ na es lʼigŋ lʼok wɛl ee? Njaŋ! Aŋke ɛm mʼel Israɛl iy, Abraham e lilaw lele Bɛnjamɛ ecʼeb ɛm ecʼɛgŋ ab.
Nyam igŋm in ecʼagŋ a eke in obi lʼikŋ anym li sↄsum lʼot a, lʼɛlum es. Eke mʼↄnym yadŋ, ke uwr <font color=blue>Eli</font> e sodad eke anŋ Nyam Lɛl ɛm ab any, yogŋ a eke nʼam ok Israɛl eyŋ dedeku es Nyam ogŋ a.
Ɛtŋ kin odad a: Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ, -lʼibi ŋ eci <font color=blue>kokoba</font> ↄb ɛsɛl a, -ni ŋuŋn ŋ e segb waw usu a. Ɛm sↄny cɛ anake mʼanŋ a, ɛtŋ ɛm yɛji -nʼam erur eke -li kʼibiʼm.<RF q=†>1 Ɛ́b Ebu 19.10,14.
Ɛtŋ Nyam ecʼeke dad ↄŋʼn a el bogŋ ecʼee? Anm ŋ sↄny! Mʼɛdŋn agŋ fandi lↄbŋ mʼɛw es ɛm eci, agŋ a eke ókm ↄwrↄkp wus igŋm Baal nuŋ a.<RF q=†>1 Ɛ́b Ebu 19.18.Baal:el ob mum nyam eke bieku ɛjeci ɛjecʼa eke ir titm Israɛl eyŋ a bʼigŋ nuŋ ɛsɛ nyàm af. Israɛl eyŋ nↄnↄ yɛji ↄb nuŋ am igŋ nyàm na nuŋ.
Yɛfɛnyna yɛji low nyam a cɛ. Agŋ tɛl anŋ eke Nyam in ecʼɛrm mamn ab ɛm ɛdŋn ɛw es.
Sica ayaf si ki dadr ab ee? Israɛl eyŋ ɛŋnm ob a eke -nʼam ↄl es a, kↄ agŋ a cɛ eke Nyam sↄsum ot a ɛŋn ob a; agŋ likpr a ↄny ɛrm tuↄtuↄ,
ɛtŋ ɛsɛ elel eke wɛl nↄn Nyam Lɛl ɛm ab af: toŋ ke igŋ yɛfɛnyna a, Nyam ↄŋ ɛl eci low iri a anŋ ɛsɛ ob eke uw af, nʼↄↄm abusu eke ɛl ecʼanyamn a kʼɛkn es, ke ɛl ecʼↄru a íri ów.<RF q=†>Ol Ɔkn 29.3; Esayi 6.10.
Ɛb ebu David yɛji dad ninɛ: Ke ɛl eci ob ij ɛgbɛl a ítŋn el meb eke wɛl uk ɛl, nↄmu e wɛl ɛdŋ, ɛl e wus ok eci, ke Nyam kók ɛl ow e low.
Ke -lʼel ány eflu, -li kʼɛknmn low kaka fɛŋ! Ke Nyam úyul ɛl ɛrɛkp leg leg ↄny ibn ɛl es sɛgŋ fɛŋ!<RF q=†>Selu 69.23-24, Sɛptant ɛm ecʼodad eke wɛl oc.
Agŋ a eke elm Jwifɛl a eci sel ɛŋn owiSica mʼam ibrm mʼɛsɛ: kↄ Jwifɛl na wus -lʼok kpɛkŋ kpɛkŋ ab ee? Njaŋ! Gbɛkↄ ɛl eci low any ↄbr a ↄŋ ɛtŋ bieku ɛjeci ecʼagŋ a ↄtu ɛŋn sel. Ɛbɛn a, ow ↄŋ Israɛl eyŋ am ogŋ ɛl ŋkre.
Israɛl eci low any ↄbr a ism wus ów amamn ɛgbɛl ɛgbɛl ab, ɛtŋ in eci wus ɛy a ism agŋ ekʼelm Jwifɛl a ów amamn ɛgbɛl ɛgbɛl ab. Sica, lɛgŋ a eke Jwifɛl a fɛŋ bʼow ɛwl ɛgŋ Nyam e low eb a, ow ayl tasi eke Nyam ecʼów amamn ɛgbɛl a ɛmɛny bʼow agb bobn.
Sica, ↄny eke elmn Jwifɛl a, ↄny anake mʼam dad ↄny odad a. Ɛm mʼel Krist ecʼ <font color=blue>ɛrm</font> ɛs agŋ a ekʼelm Jwifɛl a eci, ɛtŋ mʼↄny sos ɛm iŋn ɛm e juma na ɛm.
Juma na eci kok ɛm a, mʼam ↄny tutr eke mi bʼow mʼobn ɛm lisijimɛl Jwifɛl eci ŋkre ogŋ a, ke ow ↄ́ŋ mʼeb agŋ nyam nyam ɛl ɛm.
Tasi ɛm a, eke Nyam ɛw ɛl saw a, lʼokr ɛm wus ab. Sica, lɛgŋ a eke li bʼow lʼɛwl lʼeb wɛl a, bla lowi bʼow ɛy ab ee? Agŋ eke uw a bʼow ɛwl anŋ owr.
Eke futufutu ecʼogog nyam el Nyam eci, ke futufutu a nimum yɛji in ecʼana.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Awl 15.19-21. Ɛtŋ eke likŋ nyam eci min a fɛŋ el Nyam eci, ke ál a yɛji in ecʼana.
Israɛl eyŋ anŋ ɛsɛ olivie ikŋ eke wɛl ewl ↄgm, ke Nyam bubr in ecʼál bɛb es af. Ɛtŋ ŋ, eke elm Jwif ke anŋ ɛsɛ akp ↄfr ɛm ecʼolivie ikŋ af a, lʼoc lʼujrʼŋ likŋ lis ab ɛm, wuwlm ekŋ ál tasi a eke cucu likŋ lis a eke wɛl ewl ab ab. Ɛtŋ sica, ↄtu eke in ecʼekŋ ál ab ab kʼɛ́ŋn mij a eke bʼanŋ in e min ab ɛm ow a.
Ow sosiɛm, kʼìm ekŋ ál a ecʼany af kʼíj en! Eke erur eke kʼij en, ↄkn eke ow elm ŋ ecʼabu ɛm likŋ a e min a anm, kↄ ŋ likŋ a e min a ecʼabu ɛm anŋ.
Ŋ bʼow dad ɛsɛ: wɛl bubr ekŋ ál es ɛtŋ ɛm, wɛl oc ujrʼm likŋ lis ab ɛm.
Na low nawrɛ! Wɛl bubr ɛl es aŋke -nʼↄnym ↄmn, ɛtŋ ŋ akŋm likŋ lis ab ab, aŋke ↄny ↄmn. Ŋ kʼɛ̀w sos, kↄ erŋn anake kʼↄnyʼŋ a.
Ɛɛ, aŋke eke Nyam ɛgbm Jwifɛl eke el likŋ caŋ a ecʼál ab es, ŋ yɛji li kʼow lʼɛgbmʼŋ es.
Ɛ̀bmn nyamn ɛkn elel eke Nyam bʼɛlu in ecʼɛrm mamn ↄny lel in e tuↄtuↄ el ab ab ↄkm a: lʼɛlu in e tuↄtuↄ el a ↄkm agŋ eke ok wus a e lís, ɛtŋ lʼɛlu ɛrm mamn ↄkm ŋ e lís. Gbɛkↄ ow it eke kʼanŋ in ecʼɛrm mamn ↄny ab ɛm, ekʼow elm ɛbɛn, ŋ yɛji li bʼow lʼubrʼŋ es ɛsɛ likŋ lal af.
