Mʼerur eke mi ki nↄn ów a eke nyamgbrany a dad a, kↄ mʼiri lebl nyam dadʼm ninɛ: «Òc nyamgbrany lↄbŋ a ecʼów a eke dad a ɛw es sos ɛm; kì nↄn.»
Sica afr ɛrm ɛs a eke mʼɛkn inym es okij af lele wus af ab a, igbl lidr abu ogŋ,
ɛtŋ ij nɛny Nyam ekʼanŋ owr sɛgŋ fɛŋ ke kok afr, wus, okij lele ob fɛŋ ab a e nin ɛm. Li dad ninɛ: «Ɛmɛny Nyam kʼow ekum ij!
Kↄ wanci ab af eke lↄbŋ ɛm ecʼafr ɛrm ɛs a bʼow ↄb nuŋ am afl in e krↄkr a, yogŋ anake Nyam e low a eke lↄl es a bʼow iy nɛny ɛsɛ elel eke li dad ow e low lʼok in eci juma kok ɛsɛl ekʼel <font color=blue>kokoba</font> ↄb ɛsɛl ab af a.»
Ɛtŋ ɛmɛny lebl a eke anŋ afr ikŋ mʼiri a, am dadʼm ɛsɛ: «Ìm oc lɛl likekli a eke fig anŋ afr ɛrm ɛs a ekʼinym es okij af lele wus af ab a ecʼabu ɛm a.»
Mʼim mi titm afr ɛrm ɛs a ɛtŋ mʼibrmʼn eke li kʼoc lɛl likekli a nʼↄŋʼm. Li dadʼm ninɛ: «Òc ij. Li bʼow li dedʼŋ nɛnym ɛsɛ mow mun af, kↄ li bʼow li lolʼŋ lokm.»<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn Ezekiɛl 3.3.
Mʼoc lɛl a afr ɛrm ɛs a ecʼabu ɛm ɛtŋ mʼij. Nawrɛ, lʼɛw mrɛmrɛ ɛm e nɛnym a ɛsɛ mow mun af, kↄ eke mʼakŋ mʼɛmn a, lʼɛwʼm lolo lokm.
Ɛtŋ sica wɛl dadʼm ninɛ: «Ow it ke ɛmɛny ím ↄb Nyam e kokoba ok agŋ, ɛb ɛb, ɛbr ɛbr, lele ɛ́b ebu fɛŋ ab.»
Adaŋku yony aOw e jam a, wɛl ↄŋʼm likŋ sreŋ nyam eke wɛl bʼoc bɛbmn ob, ɛtŋ wɛl dadʼm ninɛ: «Ìm bɛbmn Nyamel gbɛl a lele <font color=blue>egb</font> waw usu ab ab, ke áwl agŋ a eke bʼigŋ Nyam nuŋ ɛm yogŋ a yɛji.
Gbɛkↄ ɛ̀w Nyamel gbɛl a e gbugŋ ab es, kì bɛbmn, aŋke wɛl oc ↄŋ Nyam any uwm ɛsɛl eke bʼow uyu ob fɛŋ af ŋuŋn ɛb lala ab ɛm toŋ awl ekŋ yony miy yony.<RF q=†>awl ekŋ yony miy yony:ow cɛ ow el sɛgŋ fandi sɛgŋ ekŋ lɛw nyahan a (Es Ɛkn 11.3), ekʼel akpo nyahan lele likpr ab (Es Ɛkn 12.14). Es Ɛkn e lɛl na ɛm, sɛgŋ na eke wɛl bi lulm ɛy a, ow bi yɛgm ɛy sɛgŋ abi a eke low ŋuŋ bʼow akm low mamn es, gbuŋ ke wus e nuŋ ɛdŋ e lɛgŋ a ów a. Es Ɛkn 12.6; Daniɛl 7.25; 12.7.
Ɛtŋ mi bʼow mʼɛrm ɛm ecʼadaŋku yony a sus niŋn mob ow. -Li bʼow -lʼↄb Nyam ecʼamani a toŋ sɛgŋ fandi sɛgŋ ekŋ lɛw nyahan.»
Adaŋku yony a el oliv ekŋ yony a lele mun al yony a ekʼanŋ wus ecʼEs Ɛw a ecʼany af a.<RF q=†>Ɛ̀kn Zakari 4.1-14.
Ekʼɛgŋ nyam am erur eke ki kok ɛl low ŋuŋ, al bʼanŋ ɛl e nɛnym a am ok ↄkm tɛtul ɛl ecʼefnu a trɛ trɛ trɛ. Ɛɛ, ɛbɛn ekʼɛgŋ fɛŋ eke bʼow ↄl ɛl e low ŋuŋ kok es a bʼow uw ana.
Adaŋku amua ↄny abusu eke kʼɛdŋn nyam eke kʼan ↄpar wus es a, sɛgŋ a nimum eke -nʼam ↄb agŋ Nyam ecʼamani a. -Nʼↄny abusu eke -li kʼitŋn mij el mebl, ɛtŋ -nʼↄny abusu yɛjʼeke -li kʼↄŋ abu ɛyr ɛrŋ ɛrŋ fɛŋ ów wus af, sakp abi a eke -li bʼerur a.<RF q=†>Bɛ̀bmn 1 Ɛ́b Ebu 17.1; Ɔkm Ok 7.17-19; 1 Samiɛl 4.8.
Gbɛkↄ ba -li bʼuwar ɛl ecʼamani ↄb a, ndey a eke bʼanŋ <font color=blue>nↄmu</font> croŋ gbɛl ab ɛm ɛy ↄkm a, bʼow ogŋ ɛl ar, akm ɛl es ke ibi ɛl.
Ɛl e sos megl ugŋn a bʼow anŋ ɛb gbɛl a ecʼɛjɛm araŋn a, yogŋ a eke wɛl ɛw ɛl Ɛs Kↄtↄkↄ olikŋ af a. Nyandrɛ ɛm e nin eke wɛl bʼɛsŋ ɛb a el Sodↄm oglog Ejipt.<RF q=†>Sodↄm:ɛb eke wɛl uw any ɛsɛ nfaci ij ecʼɛb af (Nuŋ Ɔb 19.4-11).Ejiptwus af ecʼagŋ a, wɛl uw ɛl any ɛsɛ Israɛl eyŋ eci efnu af; yogŋ anake -nʼanŋn madu ↄkr ɛm a.
Agŋ agŋ a fɛŋ, eb eb a fɛŋ, ɛbr ɛbr a fɛŋ lele ɛb ɛb a fɛŋ ab ecʼagŋ a bʼow lɛr ɛl e sos megl ugŋn a toŋ sɛgŋ nyahan lele likpr ab, ɛtŋ kʼow erurm eke wɛl kʼim ot ɛl es.
Wus ecʼagŋ a sos ɛm bʼow iŋn, ɛl e luw a eci; -li bʼow -li kok sos ɛm iŋn ɛtŋ -li bʼow -lʼaparir ob, aŋke Nyam e <font color=blue>kokoba</font> ↄb ɛsɛl yony na ↄŋ ɛl -lʼɛkn gbre nↄnↄ.
Gbɛkↄ eke sɛgŋ nyahan lele likpr ab ab ɛc a, Nyam fuf kokoba ↄb ɛsɛl yony a in ecʼowr anŋ e sel a, ɛtŋ ow igbm ɛl. Ow ↄŋ agŋ a fɛŋ eke am lɛr ɛl a erŋn ligbɛl ↄny.
Kokoba ↄb ɛsɛl yony a iri lebl tuↄtuↄ nyam ekʼanŋ afr am ikŋ dad ɛl ɛsɛ: «Ùyur owr aŋa!» Ɛtŋ ɛl ecʼefnu a fɛŋ ekʼam lɛr ɛl a ecʼany af, -lʼuyu afr e jru ɛm.
Sica yony ɛm ecʼabu ɛyr a ɛc ŋ̂. Gbɛkↄ, ɛ̀wr ɛrm! Ow kʼow ibnm ɛtŋ nyahan ɛm ecʼa yɛji bʼow ow.
